OL,3,C'Evil individuals' looking to 'provoke
OL,4,Creaction' as gravestones vandalised
OL,6,FA council leader has slammed the "evil
OL,7,Findividuals" he believes are trying to
OL,8,F"provoke a reaction in our
OL,9,Fcommunities" after Muslim gravestones
OL,10,Fwere vandalised.
OL,12,FGrey paint was poured over a number of
OL,13,Fheadstones in the Muslim section of
OL,14,FBurnley Cemetery on Monday 5 August,
OL,15,Fwith Lancashire Police treating it as
OL,16,Fa hate crime.
OL,18,FFollowing news of the attack the
OL,19,FLeader of Burnley Council, Councillor
OL,20,FAfrasiab Anwar MBE, urged the Muslim
OL,21,Fcommunity not to retaliate.
