OL,3,C'Evil individuals' looking to 'provoke
OL,4,Creaction' as gravestones vandalised
OL,6,FHe said: "What type of evil
OL,7,Findividual(s) would undertake such
OL,8,Foutrageous actions, in a sacrosanct
OL,9,Fplace of reflection, where loved ones
OL,10,Fare buried, solely intended to provoke
OL,11,Fracial tensions?
OL,13,F"We are working with the police to
OL,14,Fidentify the perpetrator(s) and to
OL,15,Fensure they are reprimanded at the
OL,16,Fearliest opportunity.
