OL,3,C'Evil individuals' looking to 'provoke
OL,4,Creaction' as gravestones vandalised
OL,6,F"With actions like this, it is
OL,7,Fextremely difficult to remain calm,
OL,8,Fbut I would urge you not to react to
OL,9,Fthe provocation."
OL,11,FLancashire Police said it was treating
OL,12,Fthe hate crime "incredibly seriously".
OL,14,FA spokesperson said: "We have launched
OL,15,Fan investigation after a report of
OL,16,Fcriminal damage in Burnley today
OL,17,F(Monday, August 5).
