OL,3,C'Evil individuals' looking to 'provoke
OL,4,Creaction' as gravestones vandalised
OL,6,F"We were called around 4.15pm to
OL,7,FBurnley Cemetery on Rossendale Road
OL,8,Fafter a report that paint had been
OL,9,Fpoured across headstones in a Muslim
OL,10,Fburial area.
OL,12,F"The investigation into this matter is
OL,13,Fvery much ongoing.
OL,15,F"We are taking this matter incredibly
OL,16,Fseriously and this is being treated as
OL,17,Fa hate crime.
